      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Number of references</strong> <div class="description">Number of references contained in the bibliography. A simple numerical count of references is given in this subfield, following
            the bibliography note.
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Used to indicate the significance of a bibliography.</div>
         </div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
