      <div class="subfield"><strong>$8 - Field link and sequence number</strong> 
        <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A:   <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control Subfields</a></em>.
        </div>
   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> -  Subfield $a of field 504 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present.
      </div>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Display Constants</strong> -  There are no display constants associated with this field. Introductory terms such as  <em>Bibliography:</em>, <em>Discography:</em>, etc. are carried in the MARC record as part of the data in the field.
      </div>
